22/Jul/16 10:19;gurwls223;It seems basically comparison between numbers and decimal, and decimals with different precision and scale were not allowed but from 2.0, this restriction was relexted.

here, https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-12070 and https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-12082

